						<div class="postbody">Usually, I'd find it unlikely that lowercase letters would be available. Since there are only 256 tiles for the whole background (unless there's mid-screen bankswitching involved), there's very little reason to waste 26 of them on letters that are already available in uppercase form... But since this game can switch between Japanese and English, and Japanese needs more characters, there might be some free space for the extra English characters.</div>

